premise_source_doc_sentence: James Adolf Israel  (  2 February 1848 -- 2 February 1926  )  was a Jewish-German surgeon who was a native of Berlin .
Established in 1996 , IndieWire  (  sometimes stylized as indieWIRE or Indiewire  )  is a film industry and review website .
As of January 19 , 2016 , Indiewire is a subsidiary of Penske Media .
It has a staff of about 20 , including publisher James Israel , and Editor-in-Chief Dana Harris .
